  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p796603/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/21/0ed2c63b2b134876d3dbaf14d3245dec.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t导读：17岁&mdash;&mdash;花样年华，豆蔻岁月，这是一个非常微妙的年纪，对于父母你会有点叛逆、对于人生你会有点好奇、对于恋爱你会有点羞涩、对于未来你会有点迷茫&hellip;&hellip;你的17岁是什么样的？</p>\n<p>\n\t小贝的大儿子竟然转眼也到了这个年纪，然而他的人生&hellip;&hellip;绝不能代表我们的&ldquo;大多数&rdquo;。这开了挂的人生，简直一言难尽&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">For the average 17-year-old, there are some well-established rites of passage: slaving away for A-levels,</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/illicit\" target=\"_blank\">illicit</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;visits to the pub, a mundane Saturday job and driving lessons in the hope your parents might buy you an old&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/banger\" target=\"_blank\">banger</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">对每个17岁的少年而言，有些公认的必经之事，像是努力通过A-level课程、去未成年人不得入内的酒吧、周六打份无聊的工以及为了让父母给买一辆旧老爷车而去学驾照。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">And, in theory, Brooklyn Beckham - eldest child of footballing legend David and former Spice Girl Victoria - is just another London sixth-former.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">而布鲁克林&middot;贝克汉姆身为足球传奇大卫&middot;贝克汉姆与英国辣妹组合前成员维多利亚的大儿子，理论上其实也只是伦敦的一名大学预科少年。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">But in reality, his life bears scant resemblance to that of a normal teenager. He has his own agent, a Mercedes sports car and a famous girlfriend.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">而现实是，他的生活和一名普通的青少年有极少的相似之处。布鲁克林有自己的经纪人，一辆梅德赛斯跑车，还有非常知名的女友。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<strong>HOLLYWOOD GIRLFRIEND好莱坞女友</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/22/a90214faba3bed19a7771ec7668ca276.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t科洛&middot;格蕾斯&middot;莫瑞兹（Chlo&euml; Grace Moretz），97年的好莱坞女星，8岁涉足演艺圈，05年凭借电影《鬼哭神嚎》获美国年轻艺人奖提名，09年《海扁王》超杀女一角让她火了起来，14年获得百大最美面孔女星第二。16年4月和小贝大儿子承认恋情后，两人出双入对，又恩爱又养眼&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t功成名就男友在侧的莫瑞兹，你以为这就是她的全部了么？错！她集万千宠爱于一生的小公举人生里，还有四个哥哥，这四个哥分别画风是这样的：</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t大哥</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/22/8eb385d0113575df063c467cceeebc80.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t二哥（演员&电影制作人&保镖）</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/22/464523c7e3923d4f0062f06319c015e3.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t三哥（演员）</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/22/0b6501b852505610af6e49377d5cb4ca.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t四哥（搞笑咖）</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/22/ce0bedb21435ec967c93b0d42be5fde9.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\tEXCUSE ME这全员帅炸天的颜值是要秒杀谁呢？！！！</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<strong>SOCIAL MEDIA KING社交媒体名流</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">While most teenagers use social media to share photos of school friends, it&rsquo;s wall-to-wall celebs for Brooklyn &mdash; Christmas lunch with Gordon Ramsay and a seat at Sir Elton John&rsquo;s wedding. He has posted pictures of himself with model Cara Delevingne, comedian James Corden and Sir Elton, who is his godfather.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">在众多青少年们用社交媒体分享学校伙伴的照片时，布鲁克林的社交媒体上可是满屏的名人。上个圣诞节，他和戈登&middot;拉姆齐（厨神）共进午餐。他还是艾尔顿&middot;约翰爵士所举办婚礼的座上宾。他已经晒过自己同超模卡拉&middot;迪瓦伊、喜剧演员詹姆斯&middot;柯登以及自己教父艾尔顿&middot;约翰爵士的合照了。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/21/f6b7d842cfedafff8ca0d7b344b9fb9e.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">He joined photo-sharing website Instagram in December 2014 and by April 2015 was telling Desperate Housewives actress Eva Longoria &mdash; his mum&rsquo;s best friend &mdash; &lsquo;race you to a million!&rsquo; He won the race comfortably and now has 7.6 million followers.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">在2014年12月布鲁克林注册了照片分享网站Instagram账号，到2015年4月他便对《绝望主妇》女星伊娃&middot;朗格利亚（同时也是他妈妈的闺蜜）炫耀道：&ldquo;挑战你的100万粉丝数！&rdquo;他轻而易举地赢了这场粉丝比拼赛，如今他的Instagram有760万的追随者。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Father David says he and Victoria&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/vet\" target=\"_blank\">vet</a>&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">all the pictures their son posts. They include many of his girlfriend Chloe, complete with soppy captions such as &lsquo;love this one&rsquo;.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">他的爸爸大卫表示自己和妻子会过目儿子发过的所有照片。他们在看过儿子女友科洛的许多照片后，还会附上&ldquo;这个不错哟&rdquo;的喜爱评语。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/21/73531d4eb4cf707cf9356df6873ed499.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<strong>NICE SET OF WHEELS豪车在手请别羡慕我</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/22/c6031ef5ac7c9429e92a037bf0c2d156.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t布鲁克林的爱车，3万7000英镑的奔驰C级（<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14.5454540252686px; line-height: normal;\">Mercedes C-Class），这个月刚过了考试拿了驾照，人生中的第一辆车&hellip;&hellip;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<strong>CAMERA ACTION掌镜</strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/22/35e2ab60059c43af1ac797f6925aa214.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t布鲁克林表示：&lsquo;I want to become a photographer<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">'.</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.2000007629395px;\">（我想当个摄影师）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/07/22/20a827af0807fa0f0ffc5a1a91fee2bf.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t巴宝莉的新一季Brit香氛系列，早在1月就公布了由布鲁克林掌镜的消息，并于Instagram上同步直播，标志着他的出道之作&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\tOMG，安安静静的当个帅模特还不够，这让我等平民如何立足&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Brooklyn has a long way to go before he matches his parents, who are worth around &pound;600 million. However, he is being managed by Simon Olivera, who is dad David&rsquo;s agent, so who knows where it will all end.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">要赶上身价近6亿英镑的父母，布鲁克林还有很长一段路要走。不过，他正由父亲大卫的经纪人西蒙&middot;奥利韦拉照看，因而没有谁晓得他最终会发展成怎样。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px !important; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-color: initial;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">In total, to date, he is estimated to have earned around &pound;250,000 and counting.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">到目前为止，布鲁克林的总身价约为25万英镑，而且呈上升趋势。</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p796603/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p796603\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jp